    "English": "Sodium is typically highly stable, but certain configurations retain the reactivity of its component ions. User is advised to wear <span class=\"name name-technology\">Hazardous Material Gauntlets</span> before handling.<br><br>Synthesized from <span class=\"name name-tradeable\">Sodium</span>.",
